==English==

===Verb===
'''ghostwrite''' (''[[intransitive]]'')
#To write under the name of another (especially [[literary]] works).
#: ''Maria '''ghostwrites''' for a living and finds it a thankless task.''

'''ghostwrite''' (''[[transitive]]'')
#To [[author]] a literary work or [[speech]] in the place of another.
#: ''Bob '''ghostwrote''' the president's address.''

